OL,3,CThe Herring Girls who helped the North
OL,4,CShields Fish Quay boom
OL,6,FKatie Cole found out about the Herring
OL,7,FGirls and the role they played in the
OL,8,Ffishing industry for
OL,10,FFrom the 18th century to the 1960s,
OL,11,Fthe Fish Quay at North Shields would
OL,12,Fbe taken over by hoards of women who
OL,13,Farrived with the herring catch between
OL,14,Fearly summer and late autumn.
OL,16,FKnown as the Herring Girls, they would
OL,17,Fgut, clean and pack the fish ready for
OL,18,Fsale while the men would be out at sea.
