OL,3,CThe Herring Girls who helped the North
OL,4,CShields Fish Quay boom
OL,6,FThe women, who were predominantly
OL,7,FScottish, would follow fishing fleets
OL,8,Fdown the east coast, stopping at each
OL,9,Fport for weeks at a time.
OL,11,FSculptor Ray Lonsdale created a statue
OL,12,Fon the quay in tribute to the work of
OL,13,Fthe Herring Girls.
OL,15,F"From what I gather, they were a very
OL,16,Fcharacterful bunch of lasses who
OL,17,Fweren't meant to be messed with," he
OL,18,Fsaid.
