OL,3,CThe Herring Girls who helped the North
OL,4,CShields Fish Quay boom
OL,6,F"It was very, very labour intensive
OL,7,Fand a lot of men were out fishing so
OL,8,Fthey couldn't get the people to work
OL,9,Fto process the herring," he said.
OL,11,F"It was a lot of argy bargy, you know,
OL,12,Fwomen can't do this and women can't do
OL,13,Fthat. But, they came and they had an
OL,14,Fimpact and it turned into a really,
OL,15,Freally good job, and was a very
OL,16,Fimportant job."
OL,18,FHe continued: "Some of them could go a
OL,19,Flot faster than men anyway. They could
OL,20,Fgut 50-60 herring a minute so that's
OL,21,Fpretty quick."
