OL,3,CThe Herring Girls who helped the North
OL,4,CShields Fish Quay boom
OL,6,F'They did all the hard work'
OL,8,FEllen Mundy's mother and great-
OL,9,Fgrandmother were Herring Girls.
OL,11,FShe has carried on the tradition and
OL,12,Fnow works at Seaview Fisheries in
OL,13,FNorth Shields, but said she could
OL,14,Fnever have endured what they did.
OL,16,F"There's no way I could've been a
OL,17,FHerring Girl," she said. "I couldn't
OL,18,Fstand with my hands in the cold water.
OL,19,FI just couldn't have done it.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/8
