OL,3,CThe Herring Girls who helped the North
OL,4,CShields Fish Quay boom
OL,6,F"There's a lot of hard work. They
OL,7,Fstood there all day in all kinds of
OL,8,Fweather. They did all the hard work,
OL,9,Freally, I think."
OL,11,FA decline in herring by the 1970s
OL,12,Fmeant that the skills of the women
OL,13,Fwere no longer needed. Some women did
OL,14,Fstay in North Shields though, where
OL,15,Fthey married and went on to have
OL,16,Ffamilies.
OL,18,FLynn Collins comes from a fishing
OL,19,Ffamily and now is part of the North
OL,20,FShields Fishermen's Heritage Project.
