OL,3,CThe Herring Girls who helped the North
OL,4,CShields Fish Quay boom
OL,6,FRecalling the bustling industry on the
OL,7,FFish Quay, she said: "From me being a
OL,8,Fkid, this place, you couldn't stand
OL,9,Fhere because it was just so busy
OL,10,Feveryday.
OL,12,F"It wasn't just a weekend thing. Every
OL,13,Fday this fish quay was mad. They said
OL,14,Fif you could drive down here, you
OL,15,Fcould drive anywhere in the world."
OL,17,FBusiness on the Fish Quay started to
OL,18,Fslow in the 1980s.
